name: Single Mattress
description:
Client in his late 60s, is currently retired and a resident at a Transitional Shelter. He had just received his keys to a rental unit and required a single SPRING mattress to aid his sleep because of his poor health. 

Seeking donor's goodwill to pay for the delivery of the mattress. Thank you.

Super single sized solid wood bed frame in perfectly functional condition - only known defects are visual at the foot of the bed per picture #1.

Mattress is also super single and relatively newer (~2 years). Comes in a protector. Can sleep two adults.
